# Vegan Banana GF Egg-Free Pancakes

Whisk @gf_flour{1%cup}, @flaxseed{1%tbsp}, @baking_powder{2.5%tsp}, -@salt{1/4%tsp}, @cinnamon{1/2%tsp|optional}.

Mix @banana{1/4%cup|mashed}, @applesauce{1/4%cup}, @vanilla{1%tsp}, @almond_milk{3/4%cup}.

Combine wet + dry gently. Rest ~{20%minutes}.

Cook 2-3 tbsp batter per pancake on medium heat until bubbles form, flip.